Now I would like to encourage  my friends here on the Guild Board to do the same.<br>
Marrow donors  are  in very short supply and are desperately needed. The chances of  being a match are 1 in 20,000 (roughly).<br>
<br>
There are a number of diseases and conditions that can be treated/cured with the donation of  Stem Cells/Marrow which gives people  a chance  at living a full life rather than living under a Death sentence.<br>
<br>
Some of these include:<br>
<br>
Leukemia in its various forms,<br>
Sickle Cell Disease<br>
Non-Hodgkin's Lymphoma  <br>
Hodgkin's Disease  <br>
<br>
Among many others.<br>
<br>
I am asking all my fellow Guildies  to join with me and become a donor, it may just save a life.<br>
<br>
<br>
For more information, call either your local Blood Bank or go <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.marrow.org"> here </a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> and read the info provided. <br>
<br>
<br>
This is something I feel personally  a great deal about for reasons of my own and  thought I would share with my Guild family.<br>
<br>
<br>
Tim <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub17.ezboard.com/bviatoresnorrathae.showUserPublicProfile?gid=vendragnborn>Ven Dragnborn</A> at: 11/20/02 3:01:13 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#445566><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub17.ezboard.com/bviatoresnorrathae.showUserPublicProfile?gid=fedral>Fedral</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Member</span><br>  Posts: 46<br> <font color=#D3D0CB>(11/20/02 4:54:55 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub17.ezboard.com/fviatoresnorrathaeviatores.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=945.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.eq-viatores.org/pics/Qiara-0418-0723.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A Public Service Announcement</span><hr size=1> OK Ven I have a few questions ... <br>
